-- Thai Kasikornbank sees 2014 home loan growth of 6 pct to 8 pct
-- By Manunphattr Dhanananphorn
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 04:33AM EDT
-- None



BANGKOK, Aug 5 (Reuters) - Thailand's fourth-largest lender, Kasikornbank <KBANK.BK>, said on Tuesday a recovery in demand in the second half of this year would help boost its housing loans to grow 6 percent to 8 percent for the whole of 2014.

